Error while reading/setting the configuration of module scripting (key: root/server/host/scripting/cgi/errorfile - file: E:downloadOffline_Android_SDKserverabyss.conf - line: 48 - col: 5)

Solution:

Create in "4.1server" folder "log" and put empty file in created folder with name "cgi.log"
